{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"Serena☀️","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AyibmWFvpS4Srx56XicwoUSTK3t5icFPJ6cYsoKtNWJmsBHSmV1yAbz6XLoo3xVCnNx45KHnmzVJPojY/0","content":"主题：投简历时，如何选择职业和行业。\n\n小明在投简历时，不知道如何选择职业和行业。就认为（1）自己没有做好职业规划，所以没法选择。但是小明（2）不知道怎么规划，即使知道怎么规划，比如搜集资料对行业和职业进行了解，也（3）不知道怎么搜集资料，（4）收集到了也认为是片面的，而不是对工作实际的认知。\n\n所以小明的根本问题是投简历时，如何选择职业和行业。他认为自己的问题是：\n（1）自己没有做好职业规划\n（2）不知道怎么规划\n（3）不知道怎么搜集资料\n（4）收集到了也认为是片面的\n\n这四个问题是递进的，所以首先小明要理解职业规划对职业和行业选择的意义是什么。其次了解如何进行职业规划，再进一步深入地根据各个步骤去解决。\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":4682,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490076525000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"球状闪电","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLCPB8632Nxuia6CTs7I9LbKdkG6NPFtfP9L6Fr0dibaM7qSNgmGkpnL2Ac6YEAnVmEsBzHAbu4IicjuQ/0","content":"主题：小明因为不能进行职业规划而迷茫。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":4594,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490056124000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"金小金","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-16","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6ibkOl3cs3WZ1N8B16l2BYCT8iaEiaFibaaNX5FewClYS6RCMfI1aj1ggiaZvP53j0TBl2K7MAJQsjTnrQ/0","content":"缺乏对相关行业和职业的了解，导致无法对自己的职业进行规划。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":2873,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489658720000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"阿一Kelly","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-07","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEgJibkeibgt642PsCibSvvByVXQzR6OeyFcmFQoxzOSd819hD5YCXLGjqbOQ5BdsgpdyXiaoo39r4ib9r/0","content":"\n\n     主题：小明不了解匹配自己的目标行业及职业，导致没有合理可行的职业规划，投简历时也是无从下手。\n\n     \n\n    ","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":2762,"ty